All Implemented Interfaces:
junit.framework.Test
public class SupportedFeaturesTest
extends TestBase

Check that each predefined MediaConfig reports accurate values in MediaConfig.getSupportedFeatures().
Most cases check that the items indicating mandatory features are present, and a few check that unwanted items are *not* present, e.g. Recorder.MAX_DURATION in MediaGroupConfig.PLAYER (there is no recorder in this MediaConfig).
Items related to optional features are not tested here.
The list of testcases, with expected values, is logged by the Logger of this class, at INFO level (set by default).
